[p]Salutations Victorians![/p][p][/p][p]Hotfix 1.9.5 is now live! Another small hotfix aimed at tackling some issues with how the AI perceives the fairness of current treaties and how it gives and receives investment rights from smaller economies.[/p][p][/p][p]Check out the full patchnotes below! Checksum is `a209`.[/p][p][/p][p]As always please report any bugs on [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/forums/victoria-3-bug-reports.1114/"][u]our bug reporting forums[/u][/url]! We have also updated the [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/known-issues-update-1-9.1786714/"][u]Known Issues post for 1.9[/u][/url] with fixed issues![/p][p][/p][p]The following changes have been made to the game compared to 1.9.4:[/p][h2]AI[/h2][list][*][p]Fixed a bug where the 'fairness of current treaties' value was being wrongly calculated, resulting in major penalties for quite fair treaties[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug where the 'fairness of current treaties' value was being applied during renegotiation[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug that made the AI unwilling to get foreign investment rights in smaller economies instead of being unwilling to *give* foreign investment rights to smaller economies[/p][/*][/list][p][/p][p]Previous Patchnotes[/p][p][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/developer-diary/victoria-3-dev-diary-151-charters-of-commerce-update-1-9-now-live.1786787/"][u]1.9.0[/u][/url] | [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-9-1-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1788517/"][u]1.9.1[/u][/url] | [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-9-2-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1791382/"][u]1.9.2[/u][/url] | [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-9-3-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1806851/"][u]1.9.3[/u][/url] | [url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-9-4-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1808146/"][u]1.9.4[/u][/url][/p]